snippet.title: Cherlloydvevo
snippet.description:
Cher Lloyd, the 25-year-old singer and songwriter is back and bolder than ever. Her highly anticipated return to music, reminding fans she is sassier than ever and ready to take the reigns with this new chapter in her career. With a legion of die-hard fans, 20 million+ combined social media followers and almost a billion views on YouTube Cher Lloyd is one of the most famous multiple-award-winning and multi-platinum-selling singer-songwriters. Since her breakout on the hit TV show X-Factor, Cher Lloyd has traversed the globe and has collaborated and shared the staged with some of the world’s biggest pop artists from Taylor Swift, Demi Lovato, One Direction, T.I 
and Will.I.Am. Just to name a few.

Unabashed and unfiltered honesty has always powered the young artist, and her instantly recognizable powerhouse voice has ignited multi-platinum smashes around the world. Check out her Channels to be part of the Cher-Lloyd-World.

Listen here: https://www.cherlloyd.de/
